data.description: Beautiful 2 bedroom, 1 bath home in the 55+ community of Valle Hermosa is looking for a new owner.  Upgraded laminate flooring, kitchen cabinets and countertops mean this home is ready to party.  Washer and dryer are included.  Two large rooms allow for all your furniture to find a new location.  The back yard is fully fenced in and has several trees to provide an oasis from a busy day.  This home has central air and heating to keep you cool in the summer and warm in the winter.  Most windows have been upgraded to dual pane for energy efficiency to keep those electric bills down.
